    <abstract id="aspace_96eb2bf0823a8de142930947f12bcdc8">Records include payroll (From Ellis, Converse &amp; Co.), outgoing correspondence, notebook of orders, weaving drafts &amp; counts, including price lists and costs, and 2 folders of miscellaneous drafts. Correspondents include H. &amp; W.H. Lewis, Laidlaw Co., &amp; Lynx Corp., all of New York City. Includes Navy contracts &amp; government bids, 1917-1934.</abstract>
